oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Groundbreaking Ceremonies for the new Residence Hall
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Ground breaking ceremonies; Invitations; Dormitories; Rozier Hall
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The groundbreaking ceremonies for what would be known as Rozier Hall featured prayers from Bishop Joseph Durick, introductions from four Brothers, and psalms sung by the Cardinal Stritch Choir.
